                p.centre.mg-bottom2 ”So the darkness shall be the light”
                p.left.mg-bottom2.
                    From 2006-2012 Joosten gave weekly Sunday yoga classes in a traditional Japanese wooden temple
                    Kannon-do (temple of Avalokitesvara) at Chizanso, Hayama Japan.
                    The experience during these meditative sessions in this unique setting over many years, has
                    strongly influenced his view on light and shadow.

